    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Georgia, MiSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>技术颠覆风险</strong></p>

  - elementId: resp-desc3
    elementType: text
    bounds: [700, 282, 516, 44]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Inter, MiSans"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      wrap: true
      text: |
        <p>应对：研发投入占比提升至12%，建立技术前沿预警机制</p>
        <p style="font-size:12px; color:#8B8C89;">责任人：CTO · 优先级：P1</p>

  # 风险 4
  - elementId: resp-num4
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [660, 344, 28, 28]
    shapeName: ellipse
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: resp-num4-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [660, 344, 28, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "Inter, MiSans"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
