  - elementId: resp-num5-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [660, 432, 28, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "Inter, MiSans"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: "5"

  - elementId: resp-title5
    elementType: text
    bounds: [700, 432, 516, 24]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Georgia, MiSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>监管合规风险</strong></p>

  - elementId: resp-desc5
    elementType: text
    bounds: [700, 458, 516, 44]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Inter, MiSans"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      wrap: true
      text: |
        <p>应对：各区域合规团队前置审查+外部法律顾问常年服务</p>
        <p style="font-size:12px; color:#8B8C89;">责任人：GC/CLO · 优先级：P2</p>

  # 数据来源
  - elementId: source-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [64, 680, 600, 20]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "$warmGray"
      fontFamily: "Inter, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>Source: 集团风险管理委员会, 2025Q1风险评估报告</p>
